data.name: plUserOnline.Help
data.value: If checked, displays user online status, overridable by user settings.

data.name: plEnableExtProfilePage.Help
data.value: If checked, users will be navigated to an outside module to view a user's community profile. If this is not checked, profiles will use the core profile page per user.

data.name: plExtProfilePageID.Help
data.value: The page which houses the profile module.

data.name: plExtProfileUserParam.Help
data.value: The URL parameter that is assoicated with the UserID necessary for user profiles.

data.name: plExtProfileParamName.Help
data.value: The URL parameter name that will be passed in combination with the value for external profile pages.

data.name: plExtProfileParamValue.Help
data.value: The URL parameter value that will be passed in combination with the name for external profile pages.
